data.description:
Available August 1st, please text me to set up a showing. Thanks!

Great spot in the upper downtown area. Walking distance to Tattooed Moose, Santi's, Goat Sheep Cow, Edmund's Oast, Revelry, 616, Lewis, Home Team, Royal and many more. Concrete kitchen counter tops, huge back deck, nice front porch and plenty of charm in this side by side duplex. One carpeted loft style bedroom, and a secluded second downstairs bedroom offer plenty of space. Hardwood floors throughout and plenty of room for storage. Stacked laundry units, with ample on street parking.
